      <title>SQL学习</title>
      <link href="/blog/2022/06/19/SQL%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/"/>
      <url>/blog/2022/06/19/SQL%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="SQL学习"><a href="#SQL学习" class="headerlink" title="SQL学习"></a>SQL学习</h1><h2 id="SQL简介-amp-通用语法-amp-分类"><a href="#SQL简介-amp-通用语法-amp-分类" class="headerlink" title="SQL简介&amp;通用语法&amp;分类"></a>SQL简介&amp;通用语法&amp;分类</h2><h3 id="SQL简介"><a href="#SQL简介" class="headerlink" title="SQL简介"></a>SQL简介</h3><p><img src="/blog/assets/image-20220519145324100.png" alt="image-20220519145324100"></p><h3 id="SQL的通用语法"><a href="#SQL的通用语法" class="headerlink" title="SQL的通用语法"></a>SQL的通用语法</h3><ol><li><p>SQL 语句可以单行或多行书写，以分号结尾。</p></li><li><p>MySQL 数据库的 SQL 语句不区分大小写，关键字建议使用大写（看个人习惯）。</p></li><li><p>注释</p><ul><li><p>单行注释：– 注释内容 或 #注释内容（MySQL 特有）</p></li><li><p>多行注释：&#x2F;* 注释 *&#x2F;</p></li></ul></li></ol><h3 id="SQL语言分类"><a href="#SQL语言分类" class="headerlink" title="SQL语言分类"></a>SQL语言分类</h3><ul><li>DDL 数据定义语言，操作数据仓库，表等</li><li>DML 数据操作语言，对表中的数据进行增删改</li><li>DQL 数据查询语言，对表中的数据进行查询</li><li>DCL 数据控制语言，对数据库进行权限控制</li></ul><h4 id="DDL-操作数据库，表…"><a href="#DDL-操作数据库，表…" class="headerlink" title="DDL 操作数据库，表…"></a>DDL 操作数据库，表…</h4><hr><h5 id="操作数据库"><a href="#操作数据库" class="headerlink" title="操作数据库"></a>操作数据库</h5><ol><li>查询</li></ol><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">show</span> databases;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="2"><li><p>创建</p><ul><li>创建数据库</li></ul> <figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">create</span> database 数据库名称;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>创建数据库（判断，如果不存在则创建）</li></ul> <figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">create</span> database if <span class="keyword">not</span> <span class="keyword">exists</span> 数据库名称;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>删除</p><ul><li>删除数据库</li></ul> <figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">drop</span> database 数据库名称;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>删除数据库（判断，如果存在则删除）</li></ul> <figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">drop</span> database if <span class="keyword">exists</span> 数据库名称;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>使用数据库</p><ul><li>使用数据库</li></ul> <figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">use 数据库名称;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>查看当前使用的数据库</li></ul> <figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> database();</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h5 id="操作数据库表"><a href="#操作数据库表" class="headerlink" title="操作数据库表"></a>操作数据库表</h5><ol><li><p>查询表</p><ul><li>查询当前数据库下所有表名称</li></ul> <figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">show</span> tables;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>查询表结构</li></ul> <figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">desc</span> 表名称;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>创建表</p><ul><li>创建表</li></ul> <figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">create</span> <span class="keyword">table</span> 表名(</span><br><span class="line">字段名<span class="number">1</span> 数据类<span class="number">1</span>,</span><br><span class="line">字段名<span class="number">2</span> 数据类<span class="number">2</span>,</span><br><span class="line">   ...</span><br><span class="line">   字段名n 数据类n,</span><br><span class="line">);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- 注意：最后一行末尾，不能加逗号</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>数据类型（数值、日期、字符串）</li></ul></li></ol><p><img src="/blog/assets/image-20220519205253879.png" alt="image-20220519205253879"></p><blockquote><p>简单使用举例</p><blockquote><p>double型</p><blockquote><p> score double(总长度，小数点后保留的位数)0~100，保留小数点后两位2</p></blockquote><blockquote><p> score double(5,2)</p></blockquote><p>char&amp;varchar</p><blockquote><p>name char(10)           10个字符空间     存储的性能高    浪费空间</p></blockquote><blockquote><p>name varchar(10)      2个字符空间       存储的性能低    节约空间<br>3. 删除表</p></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote><pre><code>- 删除表<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">drop</span> <span class="keyword">table</span> 表名;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>- 删除表时判断表是否存在<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">drop</span> <span class="keyword">table</span> if <span class="keyword">exists</span> 表名;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></code></pre><ol start="4"><li>修改表</li></ol><table><thead><tr><th align="center">操作</th><th align="center">代码</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">修改表名</td><td align="center">alter table 表名 <strong>rename to</strong> 新的表名;</td></tr><tr><td align="center">添加一列</td><td align="center">alter table 表名 <strong>add</strong> 列名 数据类型;</td></tr><tr><td align="center">修改数据类型</td><td align="center">alter table 表名 <strong>modify</strong> 列名 新的数据类型;</td></tr><tr><td align="center">修改列名和数据类型</td><td align="center">alter table 表名 <strong>change</strong> 列名 新列名 新的数据类型;</td></tr><tr><td align="center">删除列</td><td align="center">alter table 表名 <strong>drop</strong> 列名;</td></tr></tbody></table><h4 id="DML-对表中的数据进行增删改"><a href="#DML-对表中的数据进行增删改" class="headerlink" title="DML 对表中的数据进行增删改"></a>DML 对表中的数据进行增删改</h4><hr><ul><li><p>添加（insert）</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- 给指定列添加数据</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">insert</span> <span class="keyword">into</span> 表名(列名<span class="number">1</span>,列名<span class="number">2</span>,...) <span class="keyword">values</span>(值<span class="number">1</span>,值<span class="number">2</span>,...);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- 给所有列添加数据列名的列表可以省略</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">insert</span> <span class="keyword">into</span> 表名 <span class="keyword">values</span>(值<span class="number">1</span>,值<span class="number">2</span>,...);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- 批量添加数据</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">insert</span> <span class="keyword">into</span> 表名(列名<span class="number">1</span>,列名<span class="number">2</span>,...) <span class="keyword">values</span>(值<span class="number">1</span>,值<span class="number">2</span>,...),</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">insert</span> <span class="keyword">into</span> 表名(列名<span class="number">1</span>,列名<span class="number">2</span>,...) <span class="keyword">values</span>(值<span class="number">1</span>,值<span class="number">2</span>,...),</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">insert</span> <span class="keyword">into</span> 表名(列名<span class="number">1</span>,列名<span class="number">2</span>,...) <span class="keyword">values</span>(值<span class="number">1</span>,值<span class="number">2</span>,...);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- 批量添加数据</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">insert</span> <span class="keyword">into</span> 表名(列名<span class="number">1</span>,列名<span class="number">2</span>,...) <span class="keyword">values</span>(值<span class="number">1</span>,值<span class="number">2</span>,...),(值<span class="number">1</span>,值<span class="number">2</span>,...),(值<span class="number">1</span>,值<span class="number">2</span>,...);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>修改（update）</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">update</span> 表名 <span class="keyword">set</span> 列名<span class="number">1</span><span class="operator">=</span>值<span class="number">1</span>,列名<span class="number">2</span><span class="operator">=</span>值<span class="number">2</span>,... [<span class="keyword">where</span> 条件];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- 注意：修改语句中如果不加条件，则将所有数据都修改！</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- 使用：将张三性别改为女</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">update</span> stu <span class="keyword">set</span> sex<span class="operator">=</span><span class="string">&#x27;女&#x27;</span> <span class="keyword">where</span> name<span class="operator">=</span><span class="string">&#x27;张三&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- 使用：将张三的生日改为1999-12-12 分数改为99.9</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">update</span> stu <span class="keyword">set</span> birthday<span class="operator">=</span><span class="string">&#x27;1999-12-12&#x27;</span>,score<span class="operator">=</span><span class="number">99.99</span> <span class="keyword">where</span> name<span class="operator">=</span><span class="string">&#x27;张三&#x27;</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- 不加条件</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">update</span> stu <span class="keyword">set</span> sex<span class="operator">=</span><span class="string">&#x27;女&#x27;</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/blog/assets/image-20220520102023743.png"></p></li><li><p>删除（delete）</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">delete</span> <span class="keyword">from</span> 表名 [<span class="keyword">where</span> 条件];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- 注意：删除语句中如果不加条件，则将所有数据都删除！</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- 使用：删除张三这条记录</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">delete</span> <span class="keyword">from</span> stu <span class="keyword">where</span> name<span class="operator">=</span><span class="string">&#x27;张三&#x27;</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- 不添加表删空</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">delete</span> <span class="keyword">from</span> stu;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h4 id="DQL-对表中的数据进行查询"><a href="#DQL-对表中的数据进行查询" class="headerlink" title="DQL 对表中的数据进行查询"></a>DQL 对表中的数据进行查询</h4><hr><h5 id="基础查询"><a href="#基础查询" class="headerlink" title="基础查询"></a>基础查询</h5><ol><li><p>查询多个字段</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> 字段列表 <span class="keyword">from</span> 表名;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> <span class="operator">*</span> <span class="keyword">from</span> 表名;  <span class="comment">-- 查询所有数据</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>去除重复记录</p> <figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> <span class="keyword">distinct</span> 字段列表 <span class="keyword">from</span> 表名;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- 使用查询地址信息去除重复</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> <span class="keyword">distinct</span> address <span class="keyword">from</span> stu;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="operator">!</span>[image<span class="number">-20220520161743679</span>](<span class="operator">/</span>assets<span class="operator">/</span>image<span class="number">-20220520161743679.</span>png)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">3.</span> 起别名</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">``` <span class="keyword">sql</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">as</span>: <span class="keyword">as</span> 也可以省略</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- 使用查询数学成绩、英语成绩</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> name,math <span class="keyword">as</span> 数学成绩,english <span class="keyword">as</span> 英语成绩 <span class="keyword">from</span> stu;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- 也可省略</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> name,math 数学成绩,english <span class="keyword">as</span> 英语成绩 <span class="keyword">from</span> stu;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h5 id="条件查询（where）"><a href="#条件查询（where）" class="headerlink" title="条件查询（where）"></a>条件查询（where）</h5><ol><li><p>条件查询语法</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> 字段列表 <span class="keyword">from</span> 表名 <span class="keyword">where</span> 条件列表;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>条件</p></li></ol><p><img src="/blog/assets/image-20220520162620714.png" alt="image-20220520162620714"></p><h5 id="排序查询（order-by）"><a href="#排序查询（order-by）" class="headerlink" title="排序查询（order by）"></a>排序查询（order by）</h5><ol><li><p>排序查询语法</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">   <span class="keyword">select</span> 字段列表 <span class="keyword">from</span> 表名 <span class="keyword">order</span> <span class="keyword">by</span> 排序字段名<span class="number">1</span> [排序方式<span class="number">1</span>],排序字段名<span class="number">2</span> [排序方式<span class="number">2</span>]...;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"> <span class="operator">-</span> 排序方式：</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="operator">-</span> <span class="keyword">asc</span>：升序排列（默认值）</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="operator">-</span> <span class="keyword">desc</span>： 降序排序</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="operator">-</span> 注意：如果有多个排序条件，当前面的条件值一样时，才会根据第二条件进行排序👇</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  ``` <span class="keyword">sql</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">-- 查询学生信息，按照数学成绩降序排列，如果数学成绩一样，再按照英语成绩升序排列</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">select</span> <span class="operator">*</span><span class="keyword">from</span> stu <span class="keyword">order</span> <span class="keyword">by</span> math <span class="keyword">desc</span>,english <span class="keyword">asc</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">##### 聚合函数</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">1.</span> 概念：</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">   将一列数据作为一个整体，进行纵向计算。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">2.</span> 聚合函数分类</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="operator">|</span> 函数名      <span class="operator">|</span> 功能                             <span class="operator">|</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="operator">|</span> <span class="comment">----------- | -------------------------------- |</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="operator">|</span> <span class="built_in">count</span>(列名) <span class="operator">|</span> 统计数量（一般选用不为<span class="keyword">null</span>的列） <span class="operator">|</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="operator">|</span> <span class="built_in">max</span>(列名)   <span class="operator">|</span> 最大值                           <span class="operator">|</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="operator">|</span> <span class="built_in">min</span>(列名)   <span class="operator">|</span> 最小值                           <span class="operator">|</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="operator">|</span> <span class="built_in">sum</span>(列名)   <span class="operator">|</span> 求和                             <span class="operator">|</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="operator">|</span> <span class="built_in">avg</span>(列名)   <span class="operator">|</span> 平均值                           <span class="operator">|</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">3.</span> 聚合函数语法：</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">   ``` <span class="keyword">sql</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="keyword">select</span> 聚合函数名(列名) <span class="keyword">from</span> 表;</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="comment">-- 注意：null值不参与所有聚合函数运算</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h5 id="分组查询（group-by）"><a href="#分组查询（group-by）" class="headerlink" title="分组查询（group by）"></a>分组查询（group by）</h5><ol><li><p>分组查询语法</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> 字段列表 <span class="keyword">from</span> 表名 [<span class="keyword">where</span> 分组前限定条件] <span class="keyword">group</span> <span class="keyword">by</span> 分组字段名 [<span class="keyword">having</span> 分组后条件过滤];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- 注意：分组之后，查询的字段为聚合函数和分组字段，查询其他字段无任何意义</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><ul><li>where 和 having 区别：<ul><li>执行时机不一样：where 是分组之前进行限定，不满足where条件，则不参与分组，而having是分组之后对结果进行过滤。</li><li>可判断的条件不一样：where 不能对聚合函数进行判断，having可以。</li></ul></li><li>执行顺序：&#x3D;&#x3D;where &gt; 聚合函数 &gt; having&#x3D;&#x3D;</li></ul><h5 id="分页查询（limit）"><a href="#分页查询（limit）" class="headerlink" title="分页查询（limit）"></a>分页查询（limit）</h5><ol><li><p>分页查询语法</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> 字段列表 <span class="keyword">from</span> 表名 limit 起始索引 , 查询条目数;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- 起始索引：从0开始</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><ul><li>计算公式：&#x3D;&#x3D;起始索引 &#x3D; （档前页码-1）* 每页显示的条目数&#x3D;&#x3D;</li><li>tips：<ul><li>分页查询limit是MySQL的数据库方言</li><li>Oracle分页查询使用rownumber</li><li>SQL Server分页查询使用top</li></ul></li></ul><h5 id="小结"><a href="#小结" class="headerlink" title="小结"></a>小结</h5> <img src="/assets/image-20220521110042316.png" alt="image-20220521110042316" style="zoom:50%;" /><h4 id="DCL-对数据库进行权限控制"><a href="#DCL-对数据库进行权限控制" class="headerlink" title="DCL 对数据库进行权限控制"></a>DCL 对数据库进行权限控制</h4><hr><h2 id="Navicat图形化客户端工具"><a href="#Navicat图形化客户端工具" class="headerlink" title="Navicat图形化客户端工具"></a>Navicat图形化客户端工具</h2><h3 id="下载安装"><a href="#下载安装" class="headerlink" title="下载安装"></a>下载安装</h3><h3 id="激活"><a href="#激活" class="headerlink" title="激活"></a>激活</h3><h3 id="使用"><a href="#使用" class="headerlink" title="使用"></a>使用</h3><h2 id="约束"><a href="#约束" class="headerlink" title="约束"></a>约束</h2><h3 id="概述和分类"><a href="#概述和分类" class="headerlink" title="概述和分类"></a>概述和分类</h3><p><img src="/blog/assets/image-20220521111024348.png" alt="image-20220521111024348"></p><p>&#x3D;&#x3D;tips：MySQL不支持检查约束&#x3D;&#x3D;</p><h3 id="约束案例"><a href="#约束案例" class="headerlink" title="约束案例"></a>约束案例</h3><h3 id="外键约束"><a href="#外键约束" class="headerlink" title="外键约束"></a>外键约束</h3><h2 id="数据库设计"><a href="#数据库设计" class="headerlink" title="数据库设计"></a>数据库设计</h2><h3 id="多表关系实现"><a href="#多表关系实现" class="headerlink" title="多表关系实现"></a>多表关系实现</h3><h3 id="案例"><a href="#案例" class="headerlink" title="案例"></a>案例</h3><h2 id="多表查询"><a href="#多表查询" class="headerlink" title="多表查询"></a>多表查询</h2><h3 id="简介"><a href="#简介" class="headerlink" title="简介"></a>简介</h3><h3 id="内连接-amp-外连接"><a href="#内连接-amp-外连接" class="headerlink" title="内连接&amp;外连接"></a>内连接&amp;外连接</h3><h3 id="子查询"><a href="#子查询" class="headerlink" title="子查询"></a>子查询</h3><h3 id="案例-1"><a href="#案例-1" class="headerlink" title="案例"></a>案例</h3><h2 id="事务"><a href="#事务" class="headerlink" title="事务"></a>事务</h2><h3 id="简介-1"><a href="#简介-1" class="headerlink" title="简介"></a>简介</h3><h3 id="四大特征"><a href="#四大特征" class="headerlink" title="四大特征"></a>四大特征</h3>]]></content>
      
      
